PN,35401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FJersey's Assisted Dying Bill has been
OL,7,Fgiven Royal Assent, the island's
OL,8,Fgovernment has announced.
OL,10,FIt means that Jersey will become the
OL,11,Ffirst place in the British Isles to
OL,12,Flegalise the practice, which is
OL,13,Fexpected to become law "in the coming
OL,14,Fdays" when it is officially registered
OL,15,Fin the Royal Court.
OL,17,FEligible terminally ill residents will
OL,18,Fbe able to end their own lives or have
OL,19,Fthem ended by a willing healthcare
OL,20,Fprofessional.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FThe Government of Jersey states the
OL,7,FRoyal Assent, given by UK Justice
OL,8,FSecretary David Lammy, is a "critical
OL,9,Fstep in ensuring that the assisted
OL,10,Fdying service can begin operating on
OL,11,Fschedule late next year".
OL,13,FMinister for Health and Social
OL,14,FServices, Senator Tom Binet, hopes
OL,15,Fthis will be around September 2027 and
OL,16,Fsays assisted deaths will take place
OL,17,F"in a number of places, including a
OL,18,Fperson's own home".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FHe adds he is "delighted" at the
OL,7,Fapproval which "arrived without any
OL,8,Fquestions" and "probably quicker than
OL,9,Fexpected".
OL,11,FThe Isle of Man, which was the first
OL,12,Fplace in the British Isles to pass its
OL,13,Fown Assisted Dying Bill in March 2025,
OL,14,Fis still waiting for Westminster
OL,15,Fapproval.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FIts draft legislation was sent back to
OL,7,Fthe island after the Ministry of
OL,8,FJustice said it was unable to grant
OL,9,FRoyal Assent as it did not comply with
OL,10,Fthe European Convention on Human
OL,11,FRights (ECHR).
OL,13,FPoliticians there have since voted on
OL,14,Famendments to the Bill, responding to
OL,15,Fthese concerns and enhancing existing
OL,16,Fsafeguards.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FLorna Pirozzolo has incurable breast
OL,7,Fcancer and says she is "incredibly
OL,8,Frelieved" that Jersey's Bill has
OL,9,Fpassed. She told ITV Channel it
OL,10,F"proves that people can make a
OL,11,Fdifference when they engage with
OL,12,Fpolitics".
OL,14,FMichael Talibard has campaigned for
OL,15,Fassisted dying for more than a decade
OL,16,Fand says "it's quite an emotional
OL,17,Fmoment".
OL,19,F"The emotions I'm feeling now are
OL,20,Frelief and satisfaction," he adds.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FHe would like the Bill to go further
OL,7,Fin the future so those without a
OL,8,Fterminal diagnosis can access the
OL,9,Fservice.
OL,11,FHowever, concerns have been raised by
OL,12,Fsome about the impact on more
OL,13,Fvulnerable individuals who may feel
OL,14,Fpressure to end their lives. They are
OL,15,Falso concerned that the law's scope
OL,16,Fmay broaden.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FDr Gordon Macdonald from the anti
OL,7,Fassisted dying campaign group Care Not
OL,8,FKilling says: "This legislation will
OL,9,Ffundamentally alter health and
OL,10,Fpalliative care on Jersey and put the
OL,11,Flives of vulnerable people at risk,
OL,12,Fexactly as we have seen in those
OL,13,Fplaces that have introduced assisted
OL,14,Fsuicide or euthanasia.
OL,16,F"We will be consulting our lawyers to
OL,17,Fdetermine our next steps and how and
OL,18,Fwhen this dangerous law can be
OL,19,Fchallenged."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FThe island's State Assembly approved
OL,7,Fthe landmark legislation in February
OL,8,Fafter years of debate. Lawmakers voted
OL,9,Fin favour by 32 votes to 16.
OL,11,FJersey is a Crown Dependency, which
OL,12,Fsits outside of the UK with its own
OL,13,FGovernment and laws.
OL,15,FHowever, as the island's
OL,16,Fconstitutional relationship is with
OL,17,Fthe British Monarch, any new
OL,18,Flegislation still has to receive Royal
OL,19,FAssent before it formally becomes law.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FJersey's formal legislative process
OL,7,Fbegan in May 2024, when the State
OL,8,Fapproved the introduction of an
OL,9,Fassisted dying law in principal.
OL,11,FThat allowed lawmakers to create draft
OL,12,Flegislation, which was published in
OL,13,FSeptember 2025, before it was voted
OL,14,Fthrough earlier this year.
OL,16,FThe law will go a step further than
OL,17,Fsimilar legislation which ultimately
OL,18,Ffailed in the UK Parliament as it will
OL,19,Fallow a willing healthcare
OL,20,Fprofessional to deliver the lethal
OL,21,Fdose.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FThere are also differences between the
OL,7,FJersey and Isle of Man Bills - Jersey
OL,8,Fhas different residency requirements,
OL,9,Fmeaning someone could live on the
OL,10,Fisland for a shorter amount of time
OL,11,Fbefore being eligible for an assisted
OL,12,Fdeath, if they meet the rest of the
OL,13,Fcriteria.
OL,15,FWho will be eligible for an assisted
OL,16,Fdeath in Jersey?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FThe legislation will allow terminally
OL,7,Fill people who are experiencing, or
OL,8,Fexpected to experience, "unbearable
OL,9,Fsuffering" to choose to end their life
OL,10,Fwith the help of a willing medical
OL,11,Fprofessional.
OL,13,FSomeone who requests an assisted death
OL,14,Fmust make a voluntary, clearly
OL,15,Fexpressed, settled and informed choice.
OL,17,FTwo doctors will also need to sign off
OL,18,Fon the decision and there is a legal
OL,19,Fapproval process, which will take at
OL,20,Fleast two weeks.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FWho can apply?
OL,8,FHow will the assisted death be
OL,9,Fdelivered?
OL,11,FThe lethal dose can either be self-
OL,12,Fadministered or delivered by a willing
OL,13,Fmedical professional.
OL,15,FOptions for how to take the approved
OL,16,Fdrugs include swallowing and receiving
OL,17,Fan injection.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FA Care Plan will be completed by the
OL,7,Fadministering practitioner and the
OL,8,Findividual, which will set out where
OL,9,Fand how the assisted death will be
OL,10,Fcarried out.
OL,12,FThe administering practitioner will be
OL,13,Fa doctor or registered nurse who
OL,14,Fsupports the individual to develop
OL,15,Ftheir Assisted Dying Care Plan, and
OL,16,Fhelps them to either self-administer
OL,17,Fthe approved drugs or give them
OL,18,Fdirectly, and stays with the
OL,19,Findividual during their death.
OL,21,FWhat safeguards are in place?
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35414
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FAlongside the legal process, requiring
OL,7,Finformed consent from the person
OL,8,Fthemselves and two independent
OL,9,Fdoctors, there would be strict
OL,10,Fpenalties for anyone found trying to
OL,11,Funduly influence someone into or out
OL,12,Fof an assisted death.
OL,14,FCoercing an individual to end their
OL,15,Fown life under the assisted dying law
OL,16,Fwould carry a maximum prison sentence
OL,17,Fof 14 years.
OL,19,FOn the other hand, unduly influencing
OL,20,Fthem out of an assisted death would be
OL,21,Flimited to a fine.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35415
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1783703991
OL,3,CJersey's Assisted Dying Bill granted
OL,4,CRoyal Assent
OL,6,FHowever, appeals can be submitted by
OL,7,Fthird parties with a "special
OL,8,Finterest", as well as the person
OL,9,Fthemselves, and the assisted death
OL,10,Fcannot take place until this is either
OL,11,Faccepted or rejected by a Jersey court.
OL,13,FAffected by an issue raised in a
OL,14,Fstory? Here's where you can get support
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/15
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
